This is a simple GUI Calculator made using Python.

User-friendly graphical user interface (GUI).

Supports basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division, modulo.

Easy-to-use buttons for numeric input and operations.

AC button to reset the input field.

It Calculates and displays results accurately.

USAGE:

Enter numbers by clicking the number buttons (0-9).

Perform arithmetic operations by clicking the operation buttons (+, -, x, /,%).

Click the "=" button to calculate the result.

Click the "AC" button to clear the input field.

The result will be displayed in the input field.
